flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Open[Admin logs in and opens Admin Panel]
  Open --> Choice{Select category}
  Choice -->|Users & Roles| Users[Manage user accounts & roles RBAC]
  Choice -->|Master Data| Master[Manage shared catalogs & units]
  Choice -->|Logs| Logs[Query cross-department operations]
  Choice -->|Backup/Restore| Backup[Trigger backup or restore process]
  
  Users --> Submit[Submit request]
  Master --> Submit
  Logs --> Submit
  Backup --> Submit
  
  Submit --> Check{Valid & Authorized?}
  Check -->|Yes| Save[System executes & persists changes]
  Save --> LogAction[Log administrative action]
  LogAction --> Show[Show success confirmation]
  Show --> End([End])
  
  Check -->|No| Error[Display Error]
  Error --> End
